OL,3,CNo signs of water depth change where
OL,4,Cgirl drowned at water park, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAn inquest into the death of an 11-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl, who died during a
OL,9,Fbirthday party at a water park, has
OL,10,Fheard there were no signs warning
OL,11,Fabout a change in water depth in the
OL,12,Farea where she died.
OL,14,FKyra Hill died at Liquid Leisure in
OL,15,FDatchet near Windsor, Berkshire, on 6
OL,16,FAugust 2022. She had been reported
OL,17,Fmissing and was found two hours later.
