OL,4,Cgirl drowned at water park, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHer family arrived at Reading
OL,8,FCoroner's Court for the inquest today
OL,9,F(13 May 2025). Her father had
OL,10,Fpreviously vowed to uncover "the whole
OL,11,Ftruth" over her death.
OL,13,FThe Senior Berkshire Coroner, Heidi
OL,14,FConner, warned Kyra's family that the
OL,15,Finquest was going to be difficult.
OL,17,FThe water park's director has been
OL,18,Fgiving evidence and admitted there was
OL,19,Fa sign that warned of shallow water,
OL,20,Fbut not that there were parts where
OL,21,Fthe pool dropped to 4.6 metres.
